node.areas_of_interest_freeform: We are proudly vertical agnostic and anti-thematic. We like being surprised and love making contrarian bets. We target initial investments of $25k-$100k but will go as low as $10k if a round is oversubscribed. Why? If we love a founder, we want to be involved, and by being a great partner, who knows, perhaps we will earn the right to invest more in future rounds.

node.person.name: Saba Karim
node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
I believe that the future of software is for human empowerment, not replacement. Tools and technologies that helps people collaborate more, work smarter, connect deeper, empower each other, communicate further, do more faster, sell better, or have greater reach.

Think along the lines of: Collaboration and Productivity Tools, Gig Economy & Freelancing, CRMs and Personal CRMs, Social Media & Communication Platforms. Some deeper specialties include Marketplaces or products designed for Gen Z.
